eLeaP,is,an,LMS,Learning,Management,System,designed,for,both,students,and,company,trainees,Users,can,easily,create,online,courses,that,can,be,customized,branded,and,even,sold,The,LMS,automatically,tracks,each,student,s,progress,and,sends,reports,to,their,instructor,eLeaP,is,entirely,web,based,and,works,on,all,mobile,devices,The,eLeaP,API,enables,users,to,integrate,the,LMS,into,their,systems